{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "幸村 第2话 意外？师之教诲！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "为了商讨幕府和日出之国\\n今后的方针……\\n十二龙氏决定聚首以谈。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "幸村正为此次远行\\n收拾行李，然而……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "咦？毛巾哪去了？\\n还有换洗用的头巾呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "幸村大人，\\n这些杂活交给我们来做就可以了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "多谢，不过没关系。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "身为一名龙氏、一名武将……\\n至少要把自己的事情做好！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "这样啊……\\n那如果您有需要的话请随时吩咐。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "毛巾……毛巾……\\n啊，找到了！现在还差……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "聚首当日——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "到时间了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "请稍等，幸村还没到。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……\\n收拾行李花了太多时间……\\n幸儿这算是勉强赶上了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "当然是迟到了。\\n如此重要的场合……\\n你太散漫了，幸儿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "呜呜……大帅，对不起……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110346_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信长",
            "context": "好啦好啦！\\n虽说是迟到，\\n也只是迟到一点点而已！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "是啊是啊。既然人到齐了，\\n就赶快开始赶快完事吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "那么，我们开始会议吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（唉……政治什么的真听不懂……\\n要是打仗的话题，\\n倒还能听明白……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（对了，趁着还没忘，\\n赶紧复习一下已经努力\\n看了半本的兵书吧。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（唔……凡处军相敌……\\n相敌……必谨察之？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "晴明今日未能与会，\\n但已将方针意见交于我，\\n他是这样说的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（话说晴明好像说过\\n阴阳师有个什么东西能用来侦查，\\n好像是叫……嗯？叫什么来着？）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "关于此事……幸村你怎么想？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "啊！想起来了！叫式鬼！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110313_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "家康",
            "context": "嗯？幸村？\\n这跟式鬼有什么关系？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "诶！？啊……那个……\\n不、不好意思……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "唉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110346_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信长",
            "context": "哈哈哈！\\n幸村你真是个有趣的家伙！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "哎呀，终于结束了。\\n这会议可真无聊，\\n我一直都是半睡半醒状态。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "幸村，你也睡着了吧？\\n看你刚才那样就知道。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不不不，刚才那只是\\n在思考兵法，所以才不小心……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "兵法？\\n幸村你还对那种东西感兴趣吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "最近刚刚开始学的！\\n因为幸儿也想像大帅\\n那样统领千军万马！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "可是，幸儿不擅长动脑子……\\n看书也不怎么能看懂。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "这样啊。那你为什么\\n还要勉强自己去学啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110345_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "光秀",
            "context": "自己做不了的事情，\\n交给别人去做不就好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "诶！？\\n不、不可以这样啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "无论是身为龙氏，还是武将，\\n幸儿都要有所成长！\\n所以一定要好好学习兵法……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "不，光秀的话也有道理。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "大帅！？您这是什么意思！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "你能有这种渴望克服\\n短板的意志，老夫很欣赏。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "嗯！这正是幸儿从大帅\\n那里继承的热血之志！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "不过……这种欣赏仅限于\\n当你是一位“武士”之时。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "而身为统领家臣、位居人上的\\n“武将”……这样显然不行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "“武士”和“武将”所需要的……\\n不一样吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "正是。能够依赖他人，将自己不擅长之事\\n交给擅长之人去做以确保事情顺利，\\n也是“武将”不可或缺的才能。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "不过……这种事也唯有\\n值得信赖之人方可托付。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "如今的你与家臣之间，\\n又可否有这种信赖关系？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "唔……这、这……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "幸儿啊，你才成为龙氏不久。\\n像这种尚不成熟的地方，\\n老夫并不会责备于你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "但你若立志成为真正意义上的“大帅”，\\n确实有必要改变一下\\n看待事物的方法了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "啊……大帅……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "……\\n如果立志成为真正意义上的大帅吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "幸儿回来了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "您回来啦，幸村大人。\\n您一定累了吧？\\n行李就交给我来整理吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "不用，这是幸儿自己的行李——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "啊……对了，将自己不擅长之事\\n交给擅长之人……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "嗯？幸村大人？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "那……那行李可以拜托你吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "当然，乐意为您效劳。\\n那么事不宜迟……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "哇……好厉害！\\n动作娴熟又干净利落……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "那、那个！难不成……\\n你还练过武艺什么的！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "不不，您太抬举我了。\\n我只是常年照顾各位大人，\\n习惯了这些工作而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "原来是这样……\\n你经历过不少照顾人的修行啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120155_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "侍女",
            "context": "修行？呵呵，这么说也没错。\\n好了……已经整理好啦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "太谢谢你了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（这比幸儿自己做要快多了。\\n原来这就是为什么要拜托别人……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "（大帅……幸儿好像有点明白了！）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}